New review from testing: "I actually had seen the previews for this show online as well as on tv. I wanted to see it so bad I downloaded Quibi just for this show. I havent watched anything else on the app yet because I -loved- this show so much I had to make a review immediately aftet watching! I finished the season in one afternoon which is awesine that it didn't consume my whole day BUT I was so sad when it was over. I really hope Dummy is renewed for a second season. At the end of season one it feels like things are just starting to get good and then they leave you wanting more. Talk about a cliffhanger to a really good show! Season 2 hurry up...i need more Codi and Barbra!" with rating 5
